{"type":null,"faqId":9431,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00） 手机还有几百兆空间，为何一直提示内存空间不足？如何解决问题？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">用户一般看到的还有几百兆空间，一般指的是手机的内置存储空间，可以通过设置</span><span><span>-</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">存储查看，如果在后台开了大量应用，一直不关闭的话，可以导致手机的</span><span><span>RAM</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">空间很小。</span><span><span>RAM</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">空间的剩余情况可以在设置</span><span><span>&gt;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">管理应用程序，点击“正在运行”，在下方可以查看。如果该空间很小的话可能导致手机提示内存空间不足，此时可以通过以下几种方式结束掉后台运行的程序：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：长按</span><span><span>menu</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">键，调用最新运行的应用程序，点击刷子图标清除掉所有的应用。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：通过手机自带的内存清理工具，点击桌面的“一键优化”图标。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">提示内存空间不足如果是第三方</span><span><span>APK</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">运行后提示的，可能是有的</span><span><span>APK</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对手机的剩余内存空间有专门的限制，如果剩余的空间不足</span><span><span>APK</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的要求，就会有提示。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":140,"faqType":"存储与文件管理","useful":1,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"44","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Storage-File-management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396252606000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":1237,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"空间不足","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}